These kinds of conversations are going on across all 28 EU member states where we are working. Moocs like eLab Europe make it easier and more affordable for SJDP participants to have access to online courses that lead to the Europe 2020 targets. But besides giving them serious courses, the program also organizes educational activities, online protests, e-activism projects to stimulate participants to ask difficult questions and have intellectual or cultural debates with other participants.

eLab or the eBoot Camp open up many possibilities to have more educational, fun and better learning experiences. Also advanced jobscolums open up many possibilities to have more educational, fun and better learning experiences. Also advanced jobscolums and entrepreneurship blogasters report on all these initiatives.
